service.name: Parental Leave Pay
service.description: Parental Leave Pay (PPL) is a taxable payment paid at the national minimum wage for a maximum of 18 weeks under the Paid Parental Leave scheme that aims to support working parents, including full-time, part-time, self-employed, casual, contract and seasonal workers who have primary care of a newborn or adopted child.
